name: Cubotogame
description:
cuboto game : in this game a cube has some velocity in forward direction and after the certain distance level will complete . for complete the game level you should  try to escap other cub wall and not fall on to thr track .

if you collab somewhere to some cube then it automatically  restart.

for playing 

w= forward force 
s= break(reverse force)
a= right
d = left ;
